{"tid":1550991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港國旗背景色 拜託各位屌細力d","createTime":"2019-09-07T19:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T00:51:35.000Z","uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"da496f117fe9c12adb56dd8a80ad1f036d2fdee2","tid":1550991,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:39:56.000Z","msg":"我認為香港有自己國旗<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">首先個顏色要有一種意義同信念可以凝聚大家</span><br />\n<br />\n1.國際普遍認為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅色</span></span></span>代表自由和人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.而<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">藍色</span></strong></span>我認為關於我地鄰近四周都係大海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色</span></strong></span>我個人有d大中華膠<br />\n覺得幾適合我地龍的傳人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>白色</strong></span>則代表和平與平等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>[black]黑色[/black]</strong></span>係尊嚴 <br />\n不過好似唔係太開朗可能未必需要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如需要徽章請各位手足師兄再諗下辦法另外加</span><br />\n我建議加如要加 可以有3種方法<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">第一種</span> 加係正中間<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">第二種</span> 加係右上角<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">第三種</span> 加係中間偏右位置<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">另外有d圖案大家可以打橫睇<br />\n睇下順唔順眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.<span style=\"color: gold;\">比較亞洲大中華膠<br />\n味道多d</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ONDqTZD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FONDqTZD.jpg&h=f3654ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/16vwPxY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F16vwPxY.jpg&h=60934fe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gnqs7jE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGnqs7jE.jpg&h=7fef989c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/giiyirk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgiiyirk.png&h=06e70b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">2.感覺似海上國家同外國味道一d</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1KMv5bS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1KMv5bS.jpg&h=a69e05c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W8VAwRS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW8VAwRS.png&h=6087d92e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jMDyiwT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjMDyiwT.png&h=523e84c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fvta5bU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvta5bU.png&h=dcd64d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pNroFLf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpNroFLf.png&h=33fcc1c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">3.得意貪玩 唔好屌咁大力<br />\n可能加徽章係左上角或者中間會好睇d</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MuUxy5m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMuUxy5m.jpg&h=c10bfcea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3h8nbR3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3h8nbR3.png&h=3917c07d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea8e28390e2b95bee1a4824f2ea9404f980240d6","tid":1550991,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:40:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f5fc440c392aa4ecdb9b089dae3e0a624829a79","tid":1550991,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:41:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">求各位手足撚下留情 屌細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"f3b35830ccc249bd3304306418450f492e9bc45f","tid":1550991,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:42:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">求各位手足撚下留情 屌細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"4352b39a17799064e7d61c1f9095f5f81e325cc9","tid":1550991,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:42:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">求各位手足撚下留情 屌細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"57b6285f936a80cf66883009ccd98303e1bb0c80","tid":1550991,"uid":217242,"like":0,"